# Active Context

The "Active Context" is the current session focus: what's being worked on now, recent decisions, immediate next steps. A pointer to the current phase.
This is an ideological parent of the `memory-bank/tasks.md` task list, containing high-level objectives & results for the current session and phase.
This file serves a pre-computed "compacted context" to enable pausing and resuming of work - concise summaries of the current thinking, decisions, and actions.

## File

`memory-bank/activeContext.md`

## How to Create

Once the current phase and its work have been identified, this file can be filled out.

## When to Update

As work is completed and decisions are made, this file can be updated.

